The deflection δRi of joint Ri and the slope Ri with respect to spanwise direction are then obtained below
(43){δRi=2∑j=0i{∫0lj1[Mj1(x)EI∂Mj1(x)∂Mi+Tj1(x)GIp∂Tj1(x)∂Mi]dx      +∫0lj2[Mj1(x)EI∂Mj2(x)∂Mi+Tj2(x)GIp∂Tj2(x)∂Mi]dx}θi=2∑j=0i{∫0lj1[Mj1(x)EI∂Mj1(x)∂Mzi+Tj1(x)GIp∂Tj1(x)∂Mzi]dx      +∫0lj2[Mj1(x)EI∂Mj2(x)∂Mzi+Tj2(x)GIp∂Tj2(x)∂Mzi]dx}
where θi denotes the slope of Ri with respect to the spanwise direction.
